# C# / Avalonia / MVVM — Tech Stack

**Firma:** HorosCode · **Produkt:** HorosCloud

## Required Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|------------|
| UI markup | **AXAML** (Avalonia 11+) |
| Language | **C#** |
| Pattern | **MVVM** |
| ViewModels | **CommunityToolkit.Mvvm** (`ObservableObject`, `[ObservableProperty]`) |
| Styles | ResourceDictionary + `{DynamicResource}` |
| Tokens | `docs/design-memory.md` → `DesignTokens.axaml` |

## Never Use in Desktop UI Tasks

- **Never** React, JSX, TSX, Next.js
- **Never** Tailwind classes or CSS-in-JS mental models
- **Never** HTML elements (`<div>`, `<span>`)
- **Never** `@tanstack/react-query`, Zustand, or web state libraries
- **Never** inline `#RRGGBB` in Views — use tokens

## ViewModel Example

```csharp
using CommunityToolkit.Mvvm.ComponentModel;
using CommunityToolkit.Mvvm.Input;

namespace HorosCloud.Desktop.ViewModels.Previews;

public partial class HeaderPreviewViewModel : ObservableObject
{
    [ObservableProperty]
    private string _appTitle = "HorosCloud";

    [ObservableProperty]
    private string _userName = "Alex M.";

    [RelayCommand]
    private void OpenNotifications() { /* Pass 1: no-op */ }
}
```

## AXAML Binding Example

```xml
<UserControl xmlns="https://github.com/avaloniaui"
             xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
             x:Class="HorosCloud.Desktop.Views.Components.HorosHeaderBar"
             x:DataType="vm:HeaderViewModel">
  <Grid ColumnDefinitions="*,Auto" Height="56"
        Background="{DynamicResource BrushSurfaceDefault}">
    <TextBlock Grid.Column="0" Text="{Binding AppTitle}"
               VerticalAlignment="Center"
               Margin="{DynamicResource Spacing6},0" />
    <Button Grid.Column="1" Content="{Binding UserName}"
            Command="{Binding OpenProfileCommand}" />
  </Grid>
</UserControl>
```

## Project Structure

```text
Views/
  Components/     ← reusable UserControls
  Previews/       ← isolated region previews
ViewModels/
  Previews/       ← preview ViewModels with mock data
Styles/
  DesignTokens.axaml
  ControlThemes.axaml
  Components.axaml
```

## Alternatives (only if project explicitly uses them)

WinUI 3, WPF, .NET MAUI — **never** assume; default is **Avalonia**.

